data.description: Welcome to your own private retreat in the heart of nature! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a sprawling 4.97-acre lot offers the perfect balance of comfort, convenience, and serenity. Step inside and be greeted by the warm and inviting living area, complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The main level owner's retreat is a true sanctuary, offering a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Unwind and rejuvenate in the privacy of your own space, with the convenience of the secondary bedrooms located on the second floor. These bedrooms share a bathroom with a dual vanity, awaiting your personal touch to complete the flooring to your unique style and taste. The heart of the home, the spacious kitchen, is ready to bring out your inner chef. Whip up culinary delights with ease while enjoying the gorgeous views of nature surrounding the property. Working from home has never been more pleasurable with the office/workshop area adjacent to the living room. Whether you need a dedicated office space or a creative haven, this versatile area provides endless possibilities to suit your needs. This home also boasts a new septic tank system installed in June 2023 and there's no HOA! Venture outside and explore the vast 4.97-acre lot adorned with beautiful shade trees, offering respite from the summer sun. For nature enthusiasts, a wet weather creek adds to the allure of this picturesque property, promising countless opportunities for outdoor adventures, peaceful walks, and endless tranquility.
